overview: Damn!!! We didn’t know we’d get so many submissions! The YouShoot Army came out in massive numbers for this one! You knew Sean would tell it like it is, and man, does he ever!  We can’t stress enough, that these are the recollections and opinions of Sean Waltman and not necessarily KC! We don’t know whether Jenna or Chyna had more…ehh…skills.  There’s no stone unturned, and this is more of a therapy session than an interview. He lets it all out. Sean Waltman’s honesty and bravery is remarkable. Get ready for one of the most memorable editions of wrestling’s #1 shoot interview series.  All this on the one, the only…YouShoot!
title: YouShoot: Sean Waltman
